    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "As I open my eyes, I realize it’s just another day. I swear I could hear my bed call out to me to go back to sleep as I stretch out of it with all the calmness in the world."
            ],
            [
                "I then look at the clock, and sigh in relief as it barely was 10 am, not too late but not quite early either. This day was fairly tranquil, with nothing to do really… but that just can’t be right."
            ],
            [
                "I always have something to do. My phone buzzed as I wonder if there is something missing. A single message from Helpie hit me with realization."
            ],
            [
                "Hey… I was just wondering where are you? The event is going to start soon, so better hurry if you want to find a good seat!"
            ],
            [
                "THE QUICK-DATE EVENT! HOW COULD I HAVE FORGOTTEN?!?! That’s right, after this event I was 100% guaranteed to find a partner."
            ],
            [
                "And to be honest, I wanted to find love more than anything in the world. Still… I forgot about it. Maybe it was a sign..."
            ],
            [
                "But as my phone kept buzzing with Helpie’s messages, I realized there was no time to think, it was time to RUN."
            ],
            [
                "Luckily, the cafeteria where the event would take place wasn’t too far away, so it would probably take me 3 minutes to get there."
            ],
            [
                "I approach the cafeteria, and my quick steps start becoming slower and slower, just to suddenly come to a stop."
            ],
            [
                "There was this hopeless feeling that I tried to push away ever since I signed up to this… but overall, the question: ¿Am I really going to find true love here?"
            ],
            [
                "I thought you wouldn’t make it! Hurry! Let’s go and get you registered."
            ],
            [
                "As I enter the cafeteria, I couldn’t help but feel overwhelmed by all the corny hearts that conformed the decor of the place."
            ],
            [
                "It was cheesy, but I really couldn’t blame the organizers for choosing to go with a very on-the-nose theme for a dating event."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie sat me on an empty table and handed me a presentation card."
            ],
            [
                "Here… fill out this nametag so that others can know your name! Let me know when you’re done."
            ],
